subtitleNullable: Song-Album-Artist names and features data from Spotify API
descriptionNullable:
### Context

This data is from Spotify API. It was for my university project about a song recommendation program using prolog language. I processed the data and turned it to csv format


### Content

There are track name,  track id, album name and artist names as string. Other values are features of song in float type.


### Acknowledgements

I have this data thanks to Spotify API and our course assistant.
